{"tid":1411372,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實今日嘅集會好緊要","createTime":"2019-08-05T03:32:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T04:32:57.000Z","uid":167971,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0ac36eb6eda7b8bc4f8e3e480e518ed7e41b2789","tid":1411372,"uid":167971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:32:51.000Z","msg":"大家一齊罷工就係為咗表達訴求<br />\n其實基本上上晝阻塞咗交通就已經令到好多人唔洗返工<br />\n下晝開始就應該要俾人搭車去集會<br />\n集會係一個非常重要嘅方法去利用群眾施壓同宣傳<br />\n而且唔好唔記得 集會通常一人多就會召集到好多人一齊做唔同嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以希望話支持塞全日地鐵嘅巴打要三思<br />\n咁做會唔會浪費咗各區可以召集一大班人嘅機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"591399d965675572f19ae8e8651611126ff9bf0f","tid":1411372,"uid":167971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:34:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d65b9a92f355a715ca38fe36c7ba105f855a2257","tid":1411372,"uid":167971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:35:16.000Z","msg":"咁多位巴打要三思呀"},{"pid":"1dab686ca26f4b133a9df62f59ad9f256f2f5f11","tid":1411372,"uid":167971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:36:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a1c819c60fca41ea631c93892049c1587b65238c","tid":1411372,"uid":167971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:36:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"944084d5e5369172461375dfd8812744a1cb82b8","tid":1411372,"uid":167971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:36:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e782e956af3e0877790675b58c80ca15d284788","tid":1411372,"uid":167971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:46:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dc62a9bc54d11ac208b21635017a1ced0c49af80","tid":1411372,"uid":65110,"like":0,"di